      <title>金矿商 Polymetal 将以 37 亿美元出售俄罗斯子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/gold-miner-polymetal-to-sell-russian-unit-for-3-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦注册的金矿商 Polymetal International Plc 在一份声明中表示，该公司将出售其受制裁的俄罗斯子公司，交易总价值近 37 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/gold-miner-polymetal-to-sell-russian-unit-for-3-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚将转向“Swiftonomics”以增加旅游支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indonesia-will-turn-to-swiftonomics-to-boost-tourism-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚正在考虑采取更多激励措施，引入更多音乐、体育和文化活动，以吸引游客花更多钱并停留更长时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indonesia-will-turn-to-swiftonomics-to-boost-tourism-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行和渣打银行面临中国风险：未来一周的财报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/hsbc-stanchart-face-china-risks-earnings-week-ahead-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司和渣打银行可能会面临其中国房地产业务和美联储潜在转向带来的盈利压力。 Rachel Yeo 在彭博电视上有更多报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/hsbc-stanchart-face-china-risks-earnings-week-ahead-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本股市接近历史新高，日元看跌头寸增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市上涨至历史新高之际，资产管理公司将日元看跌头寸增加至一年多以来的最高水平，这表明投资者对货币风险仍持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:19:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万豪梅农谈 APEC 扩张战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/marriott-s-menon-on-apec-expansion-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万豪国际集团亚太区（不包括中国）总裁 Rajeev Menon 回顾了该地区第四季度的盈利表现并讨论了该地区的扩张战略。他与哈斯琳达·阿明就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/marriott-s-menon-on-apec-expansion-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美银证券：空头离岸人民币兑多头新元和印度卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/bofa-securities-short-cnh-against-long-sgd-inr-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美银证券亚洲外汇和利率策略联席主管 Claudio Piron 表示，他做空离岸人民币，做多新加坡元和印度卢比。他与哈斯琳达·阿明就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-19/bofa-securities-short-cnh-against-long-sgd-inr-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 停止覆盖 Paytm，直至监管问题缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/jefferies-stops-coverage-on-paytm-until-regulatory-issues-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 成为第一家放弃对 Paytm 运营商 One 97 Communications Ltd. 进行报道的大型外国券商，直到围绕这家苦苦挣扎的印度金融科技巨头的消息“稳定下来”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/jefferies-stops-coverage-on-paytm-until-regulatory-issues-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对需求的担忧挥之不去，油价从三周高点下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对需求前景的持续担忧抵消了中东持续的紧张局势，油价从三周以来的最高水平下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 23:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
